I don't have any problems soloing. I just rarely solo in PoP. I have found other places to solo, and I do just fine. I can get 1 aa in about 2 hours in UP. You don't need epic or uber gear to do that. At 65 85% of all the mobs in UP are still dark blue and the aa is still very good. I guess it all comes down to skill level. I have a 56 druid, and I have quaded. It is very boring and lacks challenge IMO but that is just me. I would much rather do something like solo king in sebillis or break some hard camp that you have never seen someone solo. <br>
<br>
Either way Rthen this need you have to be the Rebel without a Cause is just boring now. You were a very good troll back in your &quot;hay day&quot;, however you don't even do it well anymore. Mages got a slight increase in DPS you say.....<br>
<br>
