Shock of Fiery Blades is....3.0 ratio 1005dd<br>
<br>
Umm that is a large jump in ratio, and nearly a 1k jump in damage. Also with focus gear FBoT is superior to SoFB in every way even for the conjuration mage.<br>
<br>
Shock of Steel 3.0 ratio 825dd<br>
Black Steel  3.9ratio 1400dd<br>
<br>
A large jump in ratio and near 75% damage increase over Shock of Steel.<br>
<br>
Our damage shield jumped 12 points. We gained a extra point of mana regen on our lvl 58 armor spell and gained 2 more mana regen on the level 62 spell. Our level 60 water pet does around 60dps and our new water pet with summon gear tops 100dps. It mitigates damage way better and has more hps. It assinates and enrages.  All the pets regen at insane rates. Get suspend menion 2 and you can go from oom to full mana in under 2mins and keep a pet up. HoE maxed out is around 4500 extra damage every 22mins and mana free. Hello !!!Fury of Magic.......Get it, you might like it.....<br>
